    transliteration: "śhrī-bhagavān uvācha\nmayā prasannena tavārjunedaṁ rūpaṁ paraṁ darśhitam ātma-yogāt\ntejo-mayaṁ viśhvam anantam ādyaṁ yan me tvad anyena na dṛiṣhṭa-pūrvam",
    translation: "By My grace, I have shown you this supreme, radiant, universal form, which no one before you has seen.",
